Oh I'm not sure what you want to do. If you want the sound to decay one, but don't repeat you shouldn't set bit 5 of $400c. If you want the sound to be at constant volume level then you should set both bit 4 and bit 5 of $400c.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38">Bregalad</a> — Sat Apr 10, 2010 8:54 am</p><hr />
